   The numbers don't go inside the quotes, in any event you are not likely 
to get millisecond polling to work with a standard joystick, it takes more 
than a millisecond to poll one.  You might want to try <id rawjoystick> 
instead as this just polls the buttons, the joystick must conform to the 
original IBM analog joystick specification however.



